---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Curriculum Vitae">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-8">
    <header class="mb-16 border-b border-earth/20 pb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-ink tracking-tight mb-2">Sergio Uribe Guinard</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-ink-light font-sans tracking-wide uppercase mb-6 text-sm">IB-Certified Language Educator &mdash; Spanish &middot; French &middot; English &middot; Secondary &amp; Middle School</p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 font-sans text-xs text-ink/70">
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/sergiouribe" target="_blank" class="hover:text-clay transition-colors">LinkedIn</a>
        <span>&bull;</span>
        <span>Da Nang, Vietnam</span>
        <span>&bull;</span>
        <a href="https://sergiouribe.co" class="hover:text-clay transition-colors">sergiouribe.co</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-16">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xs font-sans uppercase tracking-widest text-earth mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="h-[1px] w-8 bg-earth"></span> Professional Profile
        </h2>
        <p class="font-serif text-ink-light leading-relaxed">
          IB-certified Language Educator with a Master&rsquo;s in ELE (GPA 3.8/4.0) and four years of international classroom experience across Colombia, Turkey, and Thailand. Specialised in Spanish for Secondary and Middle School learners (Grades 6&ndash;12), with a track record of outstanding engagement outcomes, DELE accreditation leadership, and 30+ original H5P/digital resources produced. Developer of NeuroSpanish, a proprietary Spanish methodology grounded in SENSUM scaffolding and Comprehensible Input. Fluent in Spanish (native C2), English (C1), and French (B2). Currently in Vietnam; available to relocate from July 2026.
        </p>
        <p class="font-sans text-sm text-earth mt-4 italic">
          &#9679; Available July 2026 &mdash; passport, degrees, police clearances obtainable on request
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xs font-sans uppercase tracking-widest text-earth mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="h-[1px] w-8 bg-earth"></span> Professional Experience
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-12">
          <div class="relative pl-6 border-l border-ink/10 hover:border-clay transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-sand border-2 border-clay"></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink">NeuroSpanish &mdash; Research &amp; Curriculum Development</h3>
              <span class="text-xs font-sans text-ink/50 uppercase tracking-wider">Nov 2025 &mdash; Present</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm font-sans text-ink-light mb-3">Da Nang, Vietnam</p>
            <ul class="font-serif text-ink-light leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-none">
              <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">Developing NeuroSpanish: a proprietary Spanish acquisition methodology built on SENSUM scaffolding, narrative immersion, and 4E Cognition; designed for IB Language Acquisition contexts.</li>
              <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">Building AI-generated Comprehensible Input pipelines and interactive H5P resources for Grades 6&ndash;12 secondary learners.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-6 border-l border-ink/10 hover:border-earth transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-sand border-2 border-ink/20"></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink">Spanish MFL Teacher &middot; IB MYP Language Acquisition</h3>
              <span class="text-xs font-sans text-ink/50 uppercase tracking-wider">Aug &mdash; Oct 2025</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm font-sans text-ink-light mb-3">UWC Thailand &middot; Phuket, Thailand</p>
            <ul class="font-serif text-ink-light leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-none">
              <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">Delivered IB MYP Spanish Language Acquisition; designed differentiated tasks for mixed-ability Secondary classes across phase levels.</li>
              <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">Served as Grade 6 Co-Advisor (Homeroom): pastoral care, social-emotional transition support, parent communication.</li>
              <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">Facilitated interdisciplinary modules including Experiential Learning and MANTAS outdoor education.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-6 border-l border-ink/10 hover:border-earth transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-sand border-2 border-ink/20"></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink">Spanish MFL Teacher</h3>
              <span class="text-xs font-sans text-ink/50 uppercase tracking-wider">Nov 2021 &mdash; Jul 2023</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm font-sans text-ink-light mb-3">Tarsus American College &middot; Tarsus, Turkey</p>
            <ul class="font-serif text-ink-light leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-none">
              <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">Designed and delivered full Spanish curriculum (A1&ndash;A2 CEFR) for 120+ students, Grades 9 &amp; Preparatory; authored all unit plans, assessments, and scope-and-sequence.</li>
              <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">Led accreditation of the region&rsquo;s first official DELE examination centre with Instituto Cervantes &mdash; a first for the province.</li>
              <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">Developed 30+ interactive H5P and web-based resources; achieved a documented 40% improvement in student engagement metrics.</li>
              <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">Implemented data-driven formative assessment via LMS, reducing feedback turnaround by 35%; presented methodology to department.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-6 border-l border-ink/10 hover:border-earth transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-sand border-2 border-ink/20"></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink">Communication &amp; Intercultural World Teacher</h3>
              <span class="text-xs font-sans text-ink/50 uppercase tracking-wider">Jan 2020 &mdash; Jul 2021</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm font-sans text-ink-light mb-3">Colegio Alvernia Bilingüe &middot; Bogotá, Colombia</p>
            <ul class="font-serif text-ink-light leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-none">
              <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">Taught English to 150+ secondary students; led cross-curricular project integrating language learning with ecological awareness.</li>
              <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">Implemented Canvas LMS assessment architecture, reducing grading turnaround by 30%.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-6 border-l border-ink/10 hover:border-earth transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-sand border-2 border-ink/20"></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-ink">Spanish and English Teacher</h3>
              <span class="text-xs font-sans text-ink/50 uppercase tracking-wider">Apr &mdash; Sep 2019</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm font-sans text-ink-light mb-3">Vicariato Apostólico de Inírida &middot; Guainía, Colombia</p>
            <ul class="font-serif text-ink-light leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-none">
              <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">Designed place-based language curriculum integrating indigenous cultural context for Primary and Secondary learners in a remote multilingual community.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xs font-sans uppercase tracking-widest text-earth mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="h-[1px] w-8 bg-earth"></span> Education
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-lg text-ink">IB Certificate in Teaching and Learning</h3>
              <p class="text-sm font-sans text-ink-light">Universidad Camilo José Cela &middot; Spain</p>
              <p class="text-sm font-sans text-ink-light">IB methodologies, CAS, TOK, Approaches to Teaching and Learning (ATL).</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-sans text-ink/50 uppercase tracking-wider">2025</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-lg text-ink">Specialisation Diploma in International Education</h3>
              <p class="text-sm font-sans text-ink-light">Universidad Camilo José Cela &middot; Spain</p>
              <p class="text-sm font-sans text-ink-light">International curriculum development and global citizenship frameworks.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-sans text-ink/50 uppercase tracking-wider">2025</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-lg text-ink">Master&rsquo;s in Teaching Spanish as a Foreign Language (ELE)</h3>
              <p class="text-sm font-sans text-ink-light">Universidad de Sevilla &middot; Spain &middot; GPA 3.8/4.0</p>
              <p class="text-sm font-sans text-ink-light italic">Thesis: The Hero&rsquo;s Journey: A Didactic Proposal from Conceptual Metaphor Theory and 4E Cognition.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-sans text-ink/50 uppercase tracking-wider">2024</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-lg text-ink">Bachelor of Education in Spanish and Foreign Languages</h3>
              <p class="text-sm font-sans text-ink-light">Universidad Pedagógica Nacional &middot; Colombia</p>
              <p class="text-sm font-sans text-ink-light">Equivalent to PGCE with QTS for non-UK trained educators. Research: Multisensory Modality for Oral Production in FLE.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-sans text-ink/50 uppercase tracking-wider">2018</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xs font-sans uppercase tracking-widest text-earth mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="h-[1px] w-8 bg-earth"></span> Languages
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline border-b border-ink/10 pb-2">
            <span class="font-serif text-ink font-medium">Spanish</span>
            <span class="font-sans text-sm text-ink-light italic">Native C2 &mdash; full academic and professional fluency; primary medium of instruction</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline border-b border-ink/10 pb-2">
            <span class="font-serif text-ink font-medium">English</span>
            <span class="font-sans text-sm text-ink-light italic">C1 Advanced &mdash; full professional fluency; IB instruction language</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline border-b border-ink/10 pb-2">
            <span class="font-serif text-ink font-medium">French</span>
            <span class="font-sans text-sm text-ink-light italic">B2 Upper-Intermediate &mdash; classroom instruction capability</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline border-b border-ink/10 pb-2">
            <span class="font-serif text-ink font-medium">Turkish</span>
            <span class="font-sans text-sm text-ink-light italic">A1 Basic &mdash; functional conversational level</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xs font-sans uppercase tracking-widest text-earth mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="h-[1px] w-8 bg-earth"></span> Teaching Skills &amp; Technology
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <ul class="font-serif text-ink-light leading-relaxed space-y-2 list-none">
            <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">IB: MYP Language Acquisition (all phases), DP Spanish B &amp; ab initio, IB PYP awareness</li>
            <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">Methodology: Comprehensible Input, CEFR A1&ndash;C2, NeuroSpanish/SENSUM (proprietary), 4E Cognition</li>
            <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">Assessment: DELE Examinations (accredited centre lead), IB criterion-referenced assessment, data-driven formative feedback, GCSE/IGCSE awareness</li>
            <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">Pastoral: Homeroom advisor, Grade 6 co-advisor, cross-cultural pastoral support</li>
          </ul>
          <ul class="font-serif text-ink-light leading-relaxed space-y-2 list-none">
            <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">LMS: Canvas, ManageBac, Moodle, Blackboard, Google Workspace</li>
            <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">EdTech: H5P (30+ resources produced), AI-generated CI pipelines, digital storytelling, interactive multimedia</li>
            <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">Programming: Python 3, HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (EdTech resource development)</li>
            <li class="pl-4 relative before:content-['–'] before:absolute before:left-0 before:text-earth">Safeguarding: Enhanced DBS-equivalent (Turkey, Thailand); police clearances available for all countries of residence</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xs font-sans uppercase tracking-widest text-earth mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="h-[1px] w-8 bg-earth"></span> Professional References
        </h2>
        <p class="font-serif text-ink-light italic">Available upon request.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
